data.text:
Ashoka has elected six Ashoka Fellows in Cameroon since 1994. Ashoka plans to launch its Youth Venture and Changemaker Schools programs in Cameroon this year.

Our Ashoka Fellows in Cameroon focus on areas such as providing citizen-led solutions that maintain the integrity of water catchment areas in urban and rural communities, increasing digital literacy, and reducing the cost of accessing information online.
